race.comment: HE'S MAGIC (2) is an honest type in the frame at 20 of 51 starts including 18 wins, the latest scoring (34.22) over 595m at Sandown. Has a good record at this journey. Looks well placed here and should prove hard to beat again. COMPTON GOLD (5) was well supported last time and rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but had to settle for the minor money, finishing a nose second (34.23) over 595m at Sandown. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Expecting another good run. PAW LOUIS (1) is mixing form lately, finishing out of the placings last time at Sandown but was a Grade 4/5 winner two back at Sandown. Has the ability and can find best this time. PAW MANNY (3) among the chances again based on last run here.
